overview: Ah, to bask in the spotlight of fame. Chasey Lain plays a top fashion model who's got it all. Looks. Money. The good life. But, what happens when the details of her wild past come back to haunt her? blackmail. Just one thing. Chasey doesn't take these things lying down ... unless she really likes you. So, more over Cindy, take a hike Claudia. This is this year's model ... and she fights fire with fire.
title: Covergirl
